7197:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       JADSTP         LL_ADC_INJ_StopConversion
7198:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
